<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann II. von Nassau-Wiesbaden-Idstein, Erzbischof von Mainz</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung für den in seinem Geleit zwischen Frankfurt am Main und Mainz gefangen genommenen Seitz Graf, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="1r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_5_r2l18">Bẏſſchoff von Meincʒ </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_5_r2l19">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns iſt fürbraht woꝛden / vvie daʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l20">Seicʒ Grafe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger in ewrem geleyte 
<del rend="strikethrough">beẏ Fran </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l21"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Frankfurt vnd Meincʒe gefangen vnd hinvveg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l22">gefürt ſeẏ <expan>woꝛde<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">von </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fürſtenlıch gnad<gap reason="illegible"/></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l25">vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu 
<add><ab facs="#facs_5_r2l24">gnediklich </ab></add> wenden wöllet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l26">dinſte willen / daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger ledig werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_5_r2l27">Als etc / das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_5" id="1r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff von Meincz </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist fürbraht worden, wie daz der Seicz Grafe,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, in ewrem geleyte
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Frankfurt und Meincze gefangen und
                        hinweg gefürt sey <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        fürstenlich gnad<app>
<note><gap reason="illegible"/></note>
</app>und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darczu <add>gnediklich</add>
                        wenden wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinste willen, daz der
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        burger, ledig werde, als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>. </ab></div>
</div></body>
